item.rel_title: EARLY ESTIMATION OF REPRODUCTION NUMBER OF COVID-19 IN VIETNAM
item.rel_abs: Reproduction number is an epidemiologic indicator that reflects the contagiousness and transmissibility of infectious agents. This paper aims to estimate the reproduction number of in the early phase of COVID-19 outbreak in Vietnam.
item.rel_authors: Bui, L. V.; Nguyen, T. T.; Nguyen, H.
